First reply to a rioter, uhh say something witty...

http://files.gamebanana.com/img/ss/srends/5180390490816.jpg

I got nothin' ;~;

One of my most memorable Jax games was one of those drawn out 50 minute games.  We were all pushing mid lane and got the inhibitor.  I pinged my team to attack top lanes inhibitor and started thumping away at it with my lantern...

_**QUADRA-KILL**{{champion:39}} _

The now split up team, with all their ultimates down, set their sights on me as I started spinning my lantern and leaped over to my first ~~attacker~~ victim.

*An enemy has been slain*{{champion:131}} 

*Double Kill* {{champion:236}} 

*Triple Kill* {{champion:37}} 

*Quadra Kill!!* {{champion:77}} 

With over 1/3 of my health still; I wasn't even bleeding.  The killer of my team  dashed in to duel me as I finally popped my ultimate and spun up my counter strike.  She knew she was fucked. 

*PEEEEENTAAA-KILLL* {{champion:39}} 

I then thumped my lantern away at the enemy nexus.  

"Imagine if I had a real weapon.."{{champion:24}}
